data.description: Enjoy this park like setting & rural flavor from your deck.  (Hargus Creek is located just behind). Yet close to amenities:  Schools, YMCA, Fairgrounds, Pickaway Trail and grocery shopping. Large bedrooms w/half Bath in Owner's Suite. Porcelain tile in the kitchen & bath gives this home a rich elegance. And with contemporary flooring & fresh paint, just move in.  The roof is only 5 years old.  Garage man door allows for easy access to the back deck & yard.  Hague Water Softener is ready to be programmed to your liking.  The shed (10x16) is perfect storage or maybe a ''She Shed''.  Gather your family around the fire ring w/some hotdogs & enjoy fall while there is still time! You can let kids be kids in this huge yard. Let the dog exercise without leaving home. Desirable area of Circleville
